pect_ratio": 0.56, "filesize_approx": 20702555, "http_headers": {"User-Agent": "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/91.0.4472.106 Safari/537.36", "Accept": "text/html,application/xhtml+xml,application/xml;q=0.9,*/*;q=0.8", "Accept-Language": "en-us,en;q=0.5", "Sec-Fetch-Mode": "navigate", "Referer": "https://www.instagram.com/"}, "video_ext": "mp4", "audio_ext": "none", "abr": 0, "vbr": 2073.729, "format": "dash-1572441013971840v - 1080x1920 (DASH video)"}], "title": "Video by emonthebrain", "description": "This is a cheat code. Give yourself permission to feel the way that you want to feel- now. \nI have a 3 step process to do this if you’re not sure how:\n \n1. Get clear on the feelings that you really want (hint: you don’t want the things you want, you want the feeling you believe those things will bring you)\n2. Make a list of reasons you already have to feel that way \n3. Make a list of things you can do NOW to cultivate those feelings \n\nUpdating your self-concept will change your life. \n\nEmbodiment !!! Pass it on. \nEm 🐬\n\n#neuroscience #embodiment", "duration": 79.866, "timestamp": 1770829772, "uploader_id": "15127229", "uploader": "Emily McDonald", "channel": "emonthebrain", "like_count": 58021, "comment_count": 528, "comments": [{"author": "robben_robstar", "author_id": "1933125815", "id": "17936774571199066", "text": "Your transforming my life", "timestamp": 1775223926}, {"author": "m888rda", "author_id": "248975862", "id": "18199480066344605", "text": "❤️", "timestamp": 1775203640}, {"author": "sylszzn", "author_id": "1574185525", "id": "18042473162759283", "text": "BELIVE it until you RECIEVE it", "timestamp": 1775067106}, {"author": "bryzzooo", "author_id": "49790752766", "id": "18098251577055036", "text": "You are the best. I love every single video that you post. Thank you so much🙏🏼🫶🏼much love from germany🙂‍↕️❤️", "timestamp": 1774966807}, {"author": "to_watch_instead_of_scrolling", "author_id": "39211957438", "id": "18336968746173004", "text": "Wowwww", "timestamp": 1774701282}, {"author": "ashleytaylorfit4", "author_id": "69270635742", "id": "18355138816232490", "text": "Live in the end -  Neville Goddard", "timestamp": 1774594206}, {"author": "vaibhav_ahuja22", "author_id": "2706971051", "id": "18572406325063697", "text": "This is actually powerful", "timestamp": 1774171891}, {"author": "craigdavis8", "author_id": "181218410", "id": "18171707311392967", "text": "Yes thank you :)", "timestamp": 1774066434}, {"author": "aromaticknight", "author_id": "1392260503", "id": "18095035400062725", "text": "Thats not science, that is insanity. This makes no sense at all and by the way, It’s called: manifestation or it’s trying to make god into a genie, to do what you want him to do. This isn’t based in reality.", "timestamp": 1774037247}, {"author": "sojasahnen8", "author_id": "76413237626", "id": "17878916598514082", "text": "Woww", "timestamp": 1773784835}], "thumbnails": [{"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/630154458_1217957327151195_4268708123339303182_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi42NDB4MTEzNi5zZHIuZjcxODc4LmRlZmF1bHRfY292ZXJfZnJhbWUuYzIifQ&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=103&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gFfIoeDvG3hK4ypwN3KwT-Da2aw0qcu3dcubYzNmnCJI_IUZ09doaJfKuy7suS2EKg&_nc_ohc=M1EoFo_arAcQ7kNvwFHQVv-&_nc_gid=wN5LdPTXTDLfhZbA1uDaCA&edm=ANTKIIoBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af1q0BblT4LlJs2_x2mLW2s2HrwFPUGcwVV5LNALil0guQ&oe=69D7A4C9&_nc_sid=d885a2", "width": 640, "height": 1136, "id": "0", "resolution": "640x1136"}, {"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/630154458_1217957327151195_4268708123339303182_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi42NDB4MTEzNi5zZHIuZjcxODc4LmRlZmF1bHRfY292ZXJfZnJhbWUuYzIifQ&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=103&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gFfIoeDvG3hK4ypwN3KwT-Da2aw0qcu3dcubYzNmnCJI_IUZ09doaJfKuy7suS2EKg&_nc_ohc=M1EoFo_arAcQ7kNvwF